title: N64 SDK 5.0 ISO
description:
This is a ISO disk image of Nintendo's official N64 Software Development Kit. It is version 5.0, I'm not sure if that's the latest,but its what I got.
I hope you have fun understanding the Dev Kit, and have fun making games for he N64!
Note: I've tested this,and most works on Windows 8.1, some need compatibility settings, some can't run. If you have a windows XP or 98, it should work fine though.
